page1.title: About Me
page1.content: I have lived in three different countries and traveled a few more. I have been student representative , translator , private tutor , short story writer, delli sandwich maker , security guard and researcher. Currently I am 90% software maker 5% writer and 5% fun. . I learned to be extrovert so I am an ambivert for a decade and half at least. I love learning new stuff.It would be cherry on the top if I could find few people to do it together. I am mostly questions statue que and like to look at a problem with different angles. (love finding a different point of view) . What matter the most to me : Modern Stoic principles ,Authenticity , Brutal honesty , learner and teacher mentality. My motivation are intrinsic as long as my basic human needs are covered. I use fastpages to make this page. .
